subproject.description:
Strengthen the fight against tuberculosis :
- To support initiatives aimed at expanding the fight against tuberculosis in an effort to reduce morbididity and mortality related to the disease;
- To improve case detection of tuberculosis and improve access to care and strenghten the capaicty of the National Program Against Tuberculosis (PNLT)

